claim: After May 2019 , the main T-Series channel had uploaded more than 13 thousand videos .
truth: The main T-Series channel primarily contains Indian music videos ( Bollywood music and Indi-pop ) as well as Bollywood film trailers , and uploads several videos every day , and has uploaded 13.3 thousand videos as of June 2019 .

claim: Less than 6,165 positive coronavirus cases had been registered in China by January 29 , 2020 .
truth: As of January 29 , 2020 , approximately 6,162 cases have been confirmed including in every province of China .

claim: During the Raiders vs Patriots game of 2014 , the score was 10-6 after Janikowski scored an over 37-yard goal .
truth: The Raiders drove to the Patriots 19 , but could n't break through , and Janikowski kicked a 38-yard field goal , trimming the deficit to 10-6 .

claim: The highest percentage of the population tested for the 2020 coronavirus by any country as of before March 24 is less than 3.3 % .
truth: As of 23 March , no country had tested more than 3 % of its population , and many countries have had official policies not to test those with only mild symptoms , such as Italy , the Netherlands , Spain , and Switzerland .

claim: Peter Taylor managed the English team at the 2013 FIFA U-20 World Cup .
truth: Lascelles has represented England at all youth international levels from under-18 to under-21.On 28 May 2013 , he was named in manager Peter Taylor 's 21-man squad for the 2013 FIFA U-20 World Cup .

claim: There were less than 6,700 cases of coronavirus in Australia with 2,994 cases in New South Wales as of 25th April 2020 due to the pandemic .
truth: As of 25 April 2020 , 6,695 cases had been reported in Australia , with the highest number of cases being in New South Wales , with 2,994 .

claim: Coronavirus has affected less than 175 countries and territories as of 20 March .
truth: As of 20 March , more than 246,000 cases of COVID-19 have been reported in over 170 countries and territories , resulting in more than 10,000 deaths and 87,000 recoveries .

claim: Pain & Gain received a rating of 49 % based on fewer than 174 reviews on Rotten Tomatoes .
truth: `` It currently holds a 49 % rating on Rotten Tomatoes based on 173 reviews , with the consensus : `` '' It may be his most thought-provoking film to date , but Michael Bay 's Pain & Gain ultimately loses its satirical edge in a stylized flurry of violent spectacles . ''

claim: The Down Jones Industrial Average fell by 6 % due to coronavirus .
truth: On 11 March , Asia-Pacific and Europe stock markets closed down , while the NASDAQ Composite and the S & P 500 both fell by 5 % and the Dow Jones Industrial Average by 6 % ( with the Dow falling to 20 % below its most recent record high set on 19 February ) .

claim: Before the 7th of October 2019 , See You Again reported 4.2 billion YouTube views .
truth: As of October 5 , 2019 , the video has received over 4.2 billion views on YouTube making it the third most viewed video on the website .

claim: Pirates of the Caribbean : Dead Men Tell No Tales was amongst the highest-grossing films of 2017 after grossing more than $ 750 million worldwide on a budget of $ 320 million .
truth: It grossed $ 794 million worldwide against a production budget between $ 230–320 million , making it one of the highest-grossing films of 2017 .

claim: Terminator : The Sarah Connor Chronicles had a total of 31 episodes by the time Syfy channel gained the rights of the series .
truth: On May 18 , 2009 , despite fan efforts , Fox entertainment president Kevin Reilly announced Fox would not renew the show for a third season.. On February 22 , 2011 , the Syfy channel announced it had gained the rights to all 31 episodes of the series , and they will be shown starting April 7 , 2011..

claim: Before 2nd April , less than 110 of the less than 130 COVID-19 deaths were from patients aged 70 and above .
truth: As of April 2 , 130 of 154 ( 84 % ) COVID-19 deaths were in patients aged 70 or older , and no one younger than 50 was known to have died from the disease in Massachusetts .

claim: Before the upgrade , Wankhede Stadium 's capacity was under 70,000 .
truth: Before the upgrade , the capacity was approximately 45,000. The Wankhede stadium has been host to numerous high profile cricket matches in the past , most notable being the 2011 Cricket World Cup Final , in which India defeated Sri Lanka by 6 wickets .

claim: Swansea City A.F.C . went undefeated against Liverpool after 2017 .
truth: Swansea City was not relegated on 13 May 2018 due to the fact they went undefeated against Liverpool in 2018 , following a 2–1 defeat to already-relegated Stoke City .
